headline: Q4 Earnings Roundup: Elanco (NYSE:ELAN) And The Rest Of The Pharmaceuticals Segment
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how pharmaceuticals stocks fared in Q4, starting with Elanco (NYSE:ELAN).
